---
title: Nan's Seared Chicken & Cauli-Potato Mash with Creamy Celery Slaw
description: Say goodbye to plain old taters in your mash because cauliflower's here and it's lending incredible low carb
qualities and texture to a once familiar side that's now a delightful companion to delicious, spiced chicken! Sorry potatoes...been there, done that.

